For paper-style j CTA:

Shared memory:

	Ksmem        : Bc x D          single
	Vsmem        : Bc x D          single

	Qsmem        : Br x D          single 
	dOsmem       : Br x D          single 

	ScoreSmem[2]: Br x Bc         double, small
	Lsmem[2]    : Br              double, small
	Deltasmem[2]: Br              double, small

	Psmem        : Br x Bc         single scratch
	dP/dS smem   : Br x Bc         single scratch

Registers:

	dKacc        : Bc x D distributed across warps
	dVacc        : Bc x D distributed across warps

Optional current scratch:

	dQpartial    : Br x D current tile only
